#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "_BASS_CONFIG_HLS_DELAY: 3 → 8 seconds\n"
#~ "CDN-backed HLS streams such as TRT produce segments every 6–8 seconds. A "
#~ "3-second live delay fell within that window, causing buffer underruns and "
#~ "audio glitches during periods of slow CDN response (e.g. live sports "
#~ "broadcasts).\n"
#~ "_monitor_loop stall counter now resets only on BASS_ACTIVE_PLAYING.\n"
#~ "Previously any state other than STALLED/STOPPED — including PAUSED — "
#~ "would reset the counter, masking transient segment fetch delays and "
#~ "slowing down stall detection.\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "_BASS_CONFIG_HLS_DELAY: 3 → 8 saniye\n"
#~ "TRT gibi CDN destekli HLS yayınlarında segment üretimi 6-8 saniyede bir "
#~ "gerçekleşiyor. 3 saniyelik delay bu pencereye sığmadığından buffer "
#~ "underrun oluşuyor ve ses bozuluyordu.\n"
#~ "_monitor_loop stall sayacı artık yalnızca BASS_ACTIVE_PLAYING durumunda "
#~ "sıfırlanıyor.\n"
#~ "Önceki davranışta PAUSED de dahil STALLED/STOPPED dışı her state sayacı "
#~ "sıfırlıyordu; bu, geçici segment gecikmelerinde stall tespitini "
#~ "geciktiriyordu.\n"

